name: Shipment Confirmation
query:
select name as "Name:Data:220",
delivery_note as "Delivery Note:Data:120",

shipping_carrier as "Shipping Carrier:Data:120",
shipping_service as "Shipping Service:Data:120",
purchase_order as "Purchase Order:Data:120",
	w_verification_flag as "Shipment Status:Data:200",
	shipment_identification_number as "Shipment Number:Data:220"
	
from `tabPacking Slip` order by creation DESC;
